response.raw:
Here is the information disseminated regarding BI tools, reports, and metadata enhancements:
<OUTPUT_TEXT>
- Tableau: New version 2022.3 released with enhanced dashboard formatting options and Salesforce connector. Enables interactive data visualization and self-service analytics.
- Power BI: Added support for deployment pipelines to streamline development of reports and dashboards from dev to test to production environments. Simplifies BI application lifecycle management.  
- Qlik Sense: Introduced "Insight Advisor" which uses AI and cognitive engine to generate insights and suggest analytics and visualizations based on the data. Accelerates data exploration and deriving insights.
- Metadata: Implemented data catalog and business glossary to centrally define and manage business terms, data elements, calculations and KPIs. Improves data governance and understanding of data across the organization.
- Reports: Created new set of standard financial reports and dashboards for revenue, expenses, and profitability analysis by product, region, and customer segment. Enables executives to monitor key business metrics and trends.
</OUTPUT_TEXT>
